  <h3>Graded Work</h3>
  
Your cumulative average is determined by graded work in the categories listed
below with the indicated weights. Details and instructions are given in
the sections that follow.

<p>
  
<table border=1 cellpadding=10>
  <tr>
    <th> Graded Item(s)</th>
    <th> Weight</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Presentations</td>
    <td>20%</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Written Problem Solutions</td>
    <td>40%</td>
  </tr>
    <tr>
    <td>Written Investigations</td>
